{"tid":2320452,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"流產嬰未足24周未符胎兒定義 殯儀館拒火化 鄺俊宇籲照顧媽媽感受檢討政策","createTime":"2020-12-10T23:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T04:36:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e294f7773442899792d579b207c9b07b134f214e","tid":2320452,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T23:18:19.000Z","msg":"陳小姐透露，殯儀館根本不會理會火化甚麼，只是按照表格辦事，但醫生無法為她簽發火化所需的證書，「亦都無（其他）人肯孭飛」，故無法進行火化。她指，曾獲告知可以去不合法的地方火化或進行寵物火化，但她不希望胎兒要與其他寵物一起進行火化，「佢哋都係人，只係一個未成長嘅人」，始終希望能有一個正式的火化爐。<br />\n<br />\n提到夭折的孩子，陳小姐一度哽咽，道：「（流產胎兒）眼耳口鼻、手手腳腳都有晒，（仲）睇到個樣添⋯⋯所以就想做好啲（殮葬）。」要再次面對失去摯愛的傷痛，絕非易事，驅使陳小姐勇敢走出來的，是對其他流產媽媽痛苦的感同身受，以及對無緣來到世界的孩子的期望。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/RMQ37CILLVGU3BKDRAKDIMVFWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2FRMQ37CILLVGU3BKDRAKDIMVFWA%2F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqUcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=1f7c7f3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201211%2FRMQ37CILLVGU3BKDRAKDIMVFWA%2F&h=999afcbf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201211/RMQ37CILLVGU3BKDRAKDIMVFWA/</a>"},{"pid":"a6c571976df8fb23040f1b5d544f5ffb056a8bca","tid":2320452,"uid":43751,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T23:20:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8b5ba2ffcf1f86f6deeb4f8c629467d9f39856e","tid":2320452,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T23:21:56.000Z","msg":"搵天主教教會有殮葬服務<br />\n埋左佢"},{"pid":"ca166e7912833a85bc421faeffd84805bc9bdebf","tid":2320452,"uid":3971,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T23:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4990baed5ae7423170287240e1017a05902753e8","tid":2320452,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T23:27:08.000Z","msg":"所以宗教都係歸一<br />\n埋葬好個小生命點都好過唔知搞幾耐<br />\n有得拎返個胎已經算好<br />\n有d胎連好好說再見機會都無<br />\n就當左係垃圾處理<br />\n<br />\n為左個孩子安魂都要接受<br />\n唔通每個宗教都要整紀念花園？"},{"pid":"b17d6b586c23bd730c884a1e4a2970924f905ee9","tid":2320452,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T00:51:44.000Z","msg":"咁M血入面粒死春 同打飛機嘅2億大軍 都係唔完整嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db023506804ade2a3d188f37a8158465d91c0f24","tid":2320452,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b17d6b586c23bd730c884a1e4a2970924f905ee9","tid":2320452,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T00:51:44.000Z","msg":"咁M血入面粒死春 同打飛機嘅2億大軍 都係唔完整嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:00:04.000Z","msg":"又偷偷地走出黎9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a432dcb5d0519104b554e88e797c3f9e239cfd05","tid":2320452,"uid":48132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:00:21.000Z","msg":"法律定義下佢個b真係唔係人喎"},{"pid":"3d85cf1e63f960b331ed65e5ebad62e30909f670","tid":2320452,"uid":100322,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b17d6b586c23bd730c884a1e4a2970924f905ee9","tid":2320452,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T00:51:44.000Z","msg":"咁M血入面粒死春 同打飛機嘅2億大軍 都係唔完整嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:03:47.000Z","msg":"去到20周其實有手有腳有鼻有眼"},{"pid":"dae757f8717081428f200ec4a619387407517b6f","tid":2320452,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:07:30.000Z","msg":"咁當醫療廢物dum落堆填區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a1779cea157c0142d48cde1533804ae383299db","tid":2320452,"uid":118988,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:10:02.000Z","msg":"比錢